# .secret-scan-allowlist — regexes (one per line) for findings to suppress.
# Format: a regex matching the "filepath:linecontent" string the scanner builds.
# Lines starting with # are comments.

# T-2060 / T-2052 — test fixture: placeholder PEM block used by cmd_hub_fingerprint
# unit test to assert error path when operator points at a key.pem instead of cert.pem.
# Not a real key; payload is the 4-byte literal "AAAA". The hit line carries
# escaped \n separators in the Rust source.
crates/termlink-cli/src/commands/infrastructure\.rs:.*BEGIN PRIVATE KEY.*AAAA.*END PRIVATE KEY
